g.text: Build k8s-ready airflow image (optionally all images in parallel).
Python major/minor version used in Airflow image for images.
Rebuilds base Airflow image before building K8S image.
Copy local sources to the image.
Use uv instead of pip as packaging tool to build the image.
Run the operation in parallel on all or selected subset of parameters.
Maximum number of processes to use while running the operation in parallel.
Space separated list of python versions used for build with multiple versions.
Skip cleanup of temporary files created during parallel run.
Whether to show resource information while running in parallel.
Whether to include outputs of successful runs (not shown by default).
If dry-run is set, commands are only printed, not executed.
Print verbose information about performed steps.
